re here?\u201d \n\u00ad  Possible clinician response: \u201cYou asked how I would feel, but it is important that I understand your \n\nfeelings right now. How often would you say that you have been bothered by feeling down, depressed, \nor hopeless during the last 2 weeks?\u201d \n\n\u2022 If the patient has difficulty with longer items, separate the item into shorter parts, and provide a chance to", "type": "Document"}}